Introduction

Lee Hyunseo, known under her stage name Leeseo, is a South Korean singer-songwriter and dancer under Starship Entertainment. She is best known as the lead dancer, sub vocalist, sub rapper and maknae of the girl group IVE.

On November 12, 2021, Leeseo was revealed as the sixth member of IVE. The group officially debuted on December 1, 2021, with their single album "ELEVEN".
